FeedPackage.Description: EppLib.NET is a .NET library implementing the Extensible Provisioning Protocol (EPP)
FeedPackage.Title: EppLib

FeedPackage.Description:
EppLib.NET provides a library that makes easy for registrars to interact with registries implementing the EPP protocol.
Our library is a complete implementation of the EPP specification. Have a look at the How to section for code examples and recipes.
We now include EPP extensions for CIRA (the .CA registry), Nominet (the .UK registry) and IIS (the .SE registry).

FeedPackage.Description:
EppLib.NET provides a library that makes easy for registrars to interact with registries implementing the EPP protocol.
Our library is a complete implementation of the EPP specification. Have a look at the How to section for code examples and recipes.
We now include EPP extensions for CIRA (the .CA registry), Nominet (the .UK registry) and IIS (the .SE registry).
FeedPackage.Summary: EppLib.NET is a .NET library implementing the Extensible Provisioning Protocol (EPP)

EPPlus 3.1.1
Visit epplus.codeplex.com for the latest information
This version contain version contains two new major features - VBA and conditional formatting
New features
VBA Create,read and write a VBA project from scratch or in a template. Add and modify modules and classes. Read and write code to documents(workbook and worksheets), modules and classes. VBA protection Code signing And more...
Conditional Formatting Apply conditional formatting on any range of cells. Choose between more than 40 different types ("beginsWith", "between", "containsText", "endsWith", "equal", "greaterThan", "greaterThanOrEqual", "iconSet3", "iconSet4", "iconSet5", "last7Days", "lastMonth" and many more)
Minor new features Picture Hyperlinks Chart Axis Titles Remove method added to Drawings collection
An a lot of bug fixes

FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
New cellstore, Formula calculation engine, Replaced EPPlus 4.0.0 Beta 2
Visit epplus.codeplex.com for the latest information
EPPlus-Create Advanced Excel spreadsheet.
This is a beta release. Please test and give us some feedback
New features
Replaced Packaging API with DotNetZip * This will remove any problems with Isolated Storage and enable multi threading
New Cell store * Less memory consumtion * Insert columns (not on the range level) * Faster row inserts,
Formula Parser * Calculates all formulas in a workbook, a worksheet or in a specified range * 100+ functions implemented * Access via Calculate methods on Workbook, Worksheet and Range objects. * Add custom/missing Excel functions via Workbook.FormulaParserManager. * Samples added to the EPPlusSamples project.
The formula parser does not support Array Formulas * Intersect operator (Space) * References to external workbooks * And probably a whole lot of other stuff as well :)
Perfomance *Of course the performance of the formula parser is nowhere near Excels.Our focus has been functionality.
Agile Encryption (Office 2012-) * Support for newer type of encryption.
Minor new features * Chart worksheets * New Chart Types Bubblecharts * Radar Charts * Area Charts * And lots of bugfixes...
Beta 2 Changes * Fixed bug when using RepeatColumns & RepeatRows at the same time. * VBA project will be left untouched if its not accessed. * Fixed problem with strings on save. * Added locks to the cellstore for access by mulitple threads. * Implemented Indirect function * Used DisplayNameAttribute to generate column headers from LoadFromCollection * Rewrote ExcelRangeBase.Copy function. * Added caching to Save ZipStream for Cells and shared strings to speed up the Save method. * Added Missing InsertColumn and DeleteColumn * Added pull request to support Date1904 * Added pull request ExcelWorksheet.LoadFromDataReader

Release Candidate changes

FeedPackage.Description:
EPPlus is a powerful library for reading and writing Excel 2007/2010 files, while it is not support converting .xlsx to other type of formats PDF, Image, CSV, XML, inserting OLE object and etc. This project is aimed to provide examples to achieve above mentioned features by using free Excel Class Library - Free Spire.XLS. There is no need to install Microsoft Excel or Office and it is easy to use both of the API together.
The main features offered by Epplus_Excel:
xlsx->csv xlsx->image Export .xlss to PDF Save .xlsx to .xls Export .xlsx to XML Insert control Insert oleobject Insert sparklines Save chart to image
FeedPackage.Title: EpplusExcel

FeedPackage.Description: Omnipage Cloud Service (OCS) is a cloud hosted web service offering digital document processing capabilities and OCR. Register at https://portal.nuancecomputing.com for OCS access key and full SDK.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: First release nuget packaging of the .NET rest client to access OCS functionality in the cloud. Current OCS release notes can be reviewed at https://portal.nuancecomputing.com/RN/03172014
FeedPackage.Summary:
OmniPage Cloud Service (OCS) is a SaaS solution that provides document processing services. The goals of OCS are to • enable no-setup usage of Nuance’s Capture SDK. • provide a ready-to-use, solid and scaling document conversion platform for ISVs. • enable the development of OCR-intensive applications for devices short on computational power. OCS is a cloud service aiming at improved scalability and reliability.
Register at https://portal.nuancecomputing.com for OCS access key and full SDK.

FeedPackage.Description: Utilities for the .NET Framework.
FeedPackage.Summary: Net Utilities is library which provides syntactic sugar over the .NET Framework.
FeedPackage.Title: AydinUtilities

FeedPackage.Description:
NetUtilities is a .NET library which provides syntactic sugar over the .NET Framework, cutting down the amount of code you have to write to achieve simple tasks.
By using NetUtilities, with just a single line of code you'll be able to: - Hash passwords using SHA1, SHA256, SHA384 or SHA512 hashing algorithms. - Generate truly random strings. - Create web requests & download files.
For examples and source code: https://github.com/AydinAdn/NetUtilities
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: Updated and removed bugs... added new methods to the Http class.
FeedPackage.Summary: Net Utilities: Achieve more with less, from Http requests to hashing algorithms. A single line of code can achieve it all(most).
FeedPackage.Title: AydinUtilities

FeedPackage.Description:
.NET Utilities unifies solutions to tasks which are unnecessarily complex / complicated, by exposing simple and effective methods which are to the point. For instance, to request a web page, this is all the code you would need:
string html = Http.Get("http://google.com");
.NET Utilities can help you keep your code cleaner and shorter by providing you with the following tools: - SHA1, SHA256, SHA384 & SHA512 hashing functions. - Random string generation. - Web Requests (GET, POST & Download). - Mail functions (SMTP).
You can find the documentation, code examples & source codes all on GitHub:
https://github.com/AydinAdn/NetUtilities
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
Added new methods to the Http class to allow clients to download files and updated the SMTP class due to bugs.
Also created a Test project which you can find on GitHub.
FeedPackage.Summary: .NET Utilities: Achieve more with less, from Http requests to hashing algorithms. A single line of code can achieve it all (well... almost).
FeedPackage.Tags: C# Http Web Smtp Mail SHA1 SHA256 SHA384 SHA512 Hash Cryptography RNG Utility Utilities
